# Cursor Screenshot MCP Package

## Project
- MCP server for Cursor IDE screenshots
- Published as npm package @kirill-markin/mcp-screenshots-cursor-ide
- Uses Puppeteer & Chrome
- Node.js/TypeScript
- Auto clipboard + paste integration
- Auto Ctrl+V/Cmd+V simulation

## Dependencies
- puppeteer
- chrome-launcher
- sharp
- img-clipboard
- @nut-tree-fork/nut-js
- @modelcontextprotocol/sdk

## Code Style
- TypeScript with strict typing
- ES modules (type: module)
- Functional over OOP
- Error handling with try/finally
- Async/await patterns

## Testing
- Manual testing only
- CLI test tool: mcp-screenshots-cursor-ide-test

## Build & Usage
- npm run build
- npm run watch (development)
- npm run inspector (testing)
- npm install -g @kirill-markin/mcp-screenshots-cursor-ide@latest (installation)
- mcp-screenshots-cursor-ide (run server)
- npx @kirill-markin/mcp-screenshots-cursor-ide@latest/mcp-screenshots-cursor-ide-test <url> (test) 